column5: I can't find any info...does anybody know if New Liskeard is an unorganized Township?
Don't believe so as it's not listed in either the East or West UNO districts of Timiskaming.    It's also now apart of Temiskaming Shores.
https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Timiskaming_District Just from that I would assume organized?
Depends on the township. We are in the Mowat Landing area and its classed as not organized.
